        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Right-sizing means matching each task to the least expensive model that meets the quality bar for that task. Because model tiers differ by 5\u201320\u00d7 in price, routing even 50% of requests to a smaller model can cut total API spend by 40\u201360%. The discipline is empirical: measure quality at each tier for your specific task distribution, not the industry average."
          }
        ]
      },
